Where services are delivered through the internet, this very occasionally involves placing small amounts of information on your device (phone, tablet or computer).
These include small files known as cookies. Most web browsers allow some control of most cookies through the browser settings.
To find out more about cookies, including how to see what cookies have been set and how to manage and delete them, visit: www.allaboutcookies.org
